law.history: Repealed 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 182, effective January 1, 1997. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 118, sec. 31, effective July 1, 1987. -- Amended 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 20, effective July 1, 1964. -- Created 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 77, sec. 8-313, effective July 1, 1960.
